		<div class="mv-create-description">
			<strong>Baking eggs in a muffin tin</strong> is the easiest way to streamline your <strong>breakfast meal prep</strong>! Once you know <strong>how to bake eggs</strong>, you&#x27;ll be amazed at how easy it is!
		</div>
